      "content": [
        {
          "anchor": "discussion",
          "level": 2,
          "text": "Discussion",
          "type": "heading"
        },
        {
          "inlineContent": [
            {
              "text": "This method allows the delegate to make an informed decision about connection authentication at once. If the delegate implements this method, it has no need to implement ",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "identifier": "doc://com.apple.documentation/documentation/foundation/nsurlconnectiondelegate/1415706-connection",
              "isActive": true,
              "type": "reference"
            },
            {
              "text": " or ",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "identifier": "doc://com.apple.documentation/documentation/foundation/nsurlconnectiondelegate/1417135-connection",
              "isActive": true,
              "type": "reference"
            },
            {
              "text": ". In fact, those other methods are not invoked (except on older operating systems, where applicable).",
              "type": "text"
            }
          ],
          "type": "paragraph"
        },
        {
          "inlineContent": [
            {
              "text": "In this method,you ",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "inlineContent": [
                {
                  "text": "must",
                  "type": "text"
                }
              ],
              "type": "emphasis"
            },
            {
              "text": " invoke one of the challenge-responder methods (",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "identifier": "doc://com.apple.documentation/documentation/foundation/urlauthenticationchallengesender",
              "isActive": false,
              "type": "reference"
            },
            {
              "text": " protocol):",
              "type": "text"
            }
          ],
          "type": "paragraph"
        },
        {
          "items": [
            {
              "content": [
                {
                  "inlineContent": [
                    {
                      "identifier": "doc://com.apple.documentation/documentation/foundation/urlauthenticationchallengesender/1411062-use",
                      "isActive": true,
                      "type": "reference"
                    },
                    {
                      "text": " ",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                }
              ]
            },
            {
              "content": [
                {
                  "inlineContent": [
                    {
                      "identifier": "doc://com.apple.documentation/documentation/foundation/urlauthenticationchallengesender/1413016-continuewithoutcredential",
                      "isActive": true,
                      "type": "reference"
                    },
                    {
                      "text": " ",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                }
              ]
            },
            {
              "content": [
                {
                  "inlineContent": [
                    {
                      "identifier": "doc://com.apple.documentation/documentation/foundation/urlauthenticationchallengesender/1414474-cancel",
                      "isActive": true,
                      "type": "reference"
                    },
                    {
                      "text": " ",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                }
              ]
            },
            {
              "content": [
                {
                  "inlineContent": [
                    {
                      "identifier": "doc://com.apple.documentation/documentation/foundation/urlauthenticationchallengesender/1414590-performdefaulthandling",
                      "isActive": true,
                      "type": "reference"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                }
              ]
            },
            {
              "content": [
                {
                  "inlineContent": [
                    {
                      "identifier": "doc://com.apple.documentation/documentation/foundation/urlauthenticationchallengesender/1417331-rejectprotectionspaceandcontinue",
                      "isActive": true,
                      "type": "reference"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                }
              ]
            }
          ],
          "type": "unorderedList"
        },
        {
          "content": [
            {
              "inlineContent": [
                {
                  "text": "Your delegate method is called on the thread where the connection is scheduled. Always call the methods above on that same thread.",
                  "type": "text"
                }
              ],
              "type": "paragraph"
            }
          ],
          "style": "important",
          "type": "aside"
        },
        {
          "inlineContent": [
            {
              "text": "You might also want to analyze ",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "code": "challenge",
              "type": "codeVoice"
            },
            {
              "text": " for the authentication scheme and the proposed credential before calling a ",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "identifier": "doc://com.apple.documentation/documentation/foundation/urlauthenticationchallengesender",
              "isActive": false,
              "type": "reference"
            },
            {
              "text": " method. You should never assume that a proposed credential is present. You can either create your own credential and respond with that, or you can send the proposed credential back. (Because this object is immutable, if you want to change it you must copy it and then modify the copy.)",
              "type": "text"
            }
          ],
          "type": "paragraph"
        }
      ],
